-10-11/ty-article/how-to-talk-to-your-children-about-the-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-1b54-df31-a99f-7fd7f1430000</link><description>我们都在尽最大努力保护我们的孩子免受新闻和互联网上可怕的可怕图像的影响，但我们需要明白，即使是很小的孩子也能敏锐地意识到周围发生的事情。以下是有关如何解决这种情况的一些实用建议</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 10:45:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/how-to-talk-to-your-children-about-the-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-1b54-df31-a99f-7fd7f1430000</guid></item><item><title>“不是以色列国防军，也不是警察。一块金属在纳哈尔奥兹救了我、我的妻子和我们的孩子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/not-the-idf-not-the-police-what-saved-my-family-in-nahal-oz-was-a-piece-of-metal/0000018b-1d7a-d2fc-a59f-dd7b0d5a0000</link><description>在大屠杀发生很久之后，数百名从纳哈尔奥兹基布兹获救的以色列人描述了恐惧，以及被遗弃的感觉。但他们想回家</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 09:36:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/not-the-idf-not-the-police-what-saved-my-family-in-nahal-oz-was-a-piece-of-metal/0000018b-1d7a-d2fc-a59f-dd7b0d5a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列援助组织将创伤专业知识带回家乡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/bringing-trauma-expertise-full-circle-back-to-israel/0000018b-1d9d-d465-abbb-1dbfea960000</link><description>以色列援助团体帮助了世界各地偏远地区的灾难受害者，但现在，他们正在离家更近的地方运用他们的技能</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 08:08:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/bringing-trauma-expertise-full-circle-back-to-israel/0000018b-1d9d-d465-abbb-1dbfea960000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡推迟与甘茨就紧急战时政府问题举行会晤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-postpones-meeting-with-gantz-over-emergency-wartime-government/0000018b-1d9a-d465-abbb-1dbeac090000</link><description>两人定于周三会面。民族团结党消息人士称：“内塔尼亚胡正在拖延、拖延、拖延。首相没有表现出任何惊慌的迹象”</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 07:34:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haar